":"有冇街坊屌狗"},{"pid":"b92fc78f6b15ec83d08736c198a80ccec9642d81","tid":1523392,"uid":280072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:50:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b53f164f561fef5881f368497f915240cc44579c","tid":1523392,"uid":227275,"like":20,"dislike":0,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:50:18.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">清洗每個狗鐵站  拆鐵行動! 旺角行先!</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n吹大雞每個站都黎個大清洗<br />\n等狗鐵永久不能運作 齊齊唔洗返工 仲正過塞機場<br />\n唔通爆黑社會麻雀館 就係極限? 黑社會定係狗鐵(政府)仆街D?<br />\n塞鐵已經無用 要直接令全港狗鐵收皮<br />\n今晚咁既下場 就係狗鐵害既 其實都唔止今晚<br />\n你估落去屌D職員有用? 咪撚玩喇<br />\n跳閘? 加價都賺返有突<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n站內鋪頭日日唔敢開 <br />\n列車運作唔到 無人坐 齊齊唔洗返工 一係排到仆街去坐巴士<br />\n無人敢再落廣告<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">清洗每個狗鐵站  拆鐵行動! 旺角行先!</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"d076f4de9113e65c07a981535d83c3a228633697","tid":1523392,"uid":124711,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:50:21.000Z","msg":"831恐襲"},{"pid":"fe2361b44a6dbc96721dd98ecc19020aed28548b","tid":1523392,"uid":165840,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:50:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4460fa9878aa7757a8f3e7c467e41bfddcab5587","tid":1523392,"uid":810,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7e571af5c446340633243349547826dd2b564976","tid":1523392,"uid":21861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:50:03.000Z","msg":"有冇街坊屌狗"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-31T15:51:00.000Z","msg":"有 但絕對唔安全<br